[SHORT DESC]
Prevents critical hits.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Prevents critical hits from occurring on all Pokemon in the user's party for five turns. Fails if this move is already in effect for the user's side.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Lucky Chant has little competitive use, and thus is rarely seen. Critical hits are rare, and there are better choices for a moveslot in most cases. Furthermore, five turns is too little for protection from critical hits to be feasible.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/safeguard">Safeguard</a> is a similar move that prevents status effects for five turns.</p>